column16: Danny Valencia grounds out, shortstop Alcides Escobar to first baseman Eric Hosmer.
Chris Parmelee flies out to left fielder Mitch Maier.
Michael Cuddyer flies out to right fielder Lorenzo Cain.
Delmon Young grounds out softly, pitcher Kelvin Herrera to first baseman Eric Hosmer.
Don Kelly homers (6) on a fly ball to right field.    Danny Worth scores.
Austin Jackson flies out to right fielder Jeff Francoeur.
Brandon Inge out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Kelvin Herrera to second baseman Johnny Giavotella.    Danny Worth to 3rd.
Miguel Cabrera doubles (45) on a soft line drive to right fielder Jeff Francoeur.    Ryan Raburn scores.
